	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Was curious if anyone had written a Test Mode for the NES to make sure the HW is running ok.   Anything like that available with Source?
<br />
<br />Looking for something that would test onboard RAM for the CPU and PPU specifically.  Would be nice if there was an all inclusive one where you could test for Controller Inputs, Display PPU Palette, Sound, and probably some other stuff I'm missing.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


