	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">2600 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Was curious if anyone had written a Test Mode for the NES to make sure the HW is running ok.   Anything like that available with Source?</div>
<br />A couple existing dumps of NES diagnostic carts exist. These were used by Nintendo authorized service centers to determine the cause of hardware failure. (These are also entirely distinct from the test cases used to measure an emulator's accuracy.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


